<title>UK: Avon Rubber H1 pretax profit declines.</title>
<headline>Avon Rubber H1 pretax profit declines.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months to March 29.</p>
<p>			   (million stg unless stated)</p>
<p> Shr (pence)		 20.6		  vs   16.6</p>
<p> Dividend (pence)	   6.15		 vs    5.75</p>
<p> Pretax			 8.5*		 vs   10.2</p>
<p> Turnover		   165.5		  vs  172.1</p>
<p>NOTE - The profits mentioned in the table are pretax, pre-exceptional items. The group's pretax profit including exceptionals stood at 15.6 million stg. The company made an exceptional net gain of 11.1 million stg from sale of its tyre division.</p>
<p>Full company name - Avon Rubber Plc.</p>
<p>--London Newsroom +44 171 542 4366</p>
